How to cite
===========

big_bath is free to use under the GNU General Public License.
See LICENSE file for more details.

If you use any part of the code in a publication,
please cite it as follows:

R. Guichard, big_bath: Fortran library for spin decoherence
http://www.github/UCLGuichard/big_bath.

Here is the BibTeX entry:

```text
@misc{DECOHERENCE,
  title = {big_bath: Fortran library for spin decoherence},
  author = {Guichard, R.},
  howpublished = {\url{http://www.github/UCLGuichard/big_bath}},
  year = {2015}
}
```
